{"abstract": "Volkswagen\u2019s unbridled ambition \u2014 aiming to triple sales in a decade and overtake top carmaker Toyota \u2014 is central to what is shaping up to be one of the great corporate scandals of the age.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/27/business/as-vw-pushed-to-be-no-1-ambitions-fueled-a-scandal.html", "snippet": "Volkswagen\u2019s unbridled ambition \u2014 aiming to triple sales in a decade and overtake top carmaker Toyota \u2014 is central to what is shaping up to be one of the great corporate scandals of the age.", "lead_paragraph": "Martin Winterkorn, Volkswagen\u2019s chief executive, took the stage four years ago at the automaker\u2019s new plant in Chattanooga, Tenn., and outlined a bold strategy. The company, he said, was in the midst of a plan to more than triple its sales in the United States in just a decade \u2014 setting it on a course to sweep by Toyota to become the world\u2019s largest automaker.", "print_section": "A", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/09/27/business/27VOLKSWAGENjp1/27VOLKSWAGENjp1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 360, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/09/27/business/27VOLKSWAGENjp1/27VOLKSWAGENjp1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 360}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/09/27/business/27VOLKSWAGENjp1/27VOLKSWAGENjp1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 615, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/09/27/business/27VOLKSWAGENjp1/27VOLKSWAGENjp1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1229, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption